title: Who’s That Girl: From ‘Attack of the 50 Foot Cheerleader?’ (31 HQ Photos)
text:
View as Slideshow 1 
Welcome to the Who’s That Girl? , where we track down a lovely lady that we’ve all seen, but may not know much about, and bring you a sexy original shoot with her. Why? Because we love you, that’s why. 
Who she is: Jena Sims 
Where you’ve seen her: The sexy actress from ‘Attack of the 50 Foot Cheerleader’ and ‘3-Headed Shark Attack.’ 2 
Where you can see more of her: Her Instagram and her Twitter Machine . Sims also runs The Pageant of Hope , a charity that aims to raise awareness and support in giving children who face serious challenges the opportunity to shine and be celebrated for who they are. 3
